  "title": "嵌入野生动物纪录片视频",
  "description_md": "在网页中嵌入一段野生动物纪录片视频。\n\n- 使用 `<video>` 标签，并启用 `controls`\n- 添加 `<source>`，类型为 `video/mp4`\n- 设置视频宽度为 `100%`\n- 提供备用文本提示浏览器不支持视频播放",
  "start_code": {
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>野生动物纪录片 Demo</title>\n  <style>\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #006400, #00aa00);\n      color: #fff;\n    }\n    .card {\n      border-radius: 10px;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n      background-color: #004d00;\n      width: 200px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .card-content {\n      padding: 1rem;\n    }\n    .card-container {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 1rem;\n    }\n    header {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 1rem 2rem;\n      background-color: #004d00;\n    }\n    header h1 {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 1.8rem;\n      color: #adff2f;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1 style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">野生动物纪录片展示</h1>\n    <nav>\n      <button style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">动物分类</button>\n      <button style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">查找动物</button>\n      <button style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">纪录片列表</button>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n  <section class=\"features\">\n    <div class=\"search-bar\">\n      <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"搜索动物名称\" id=\"searchInput\">\n      <select>\n        <option>选择类别</option>\n        <option>哺乳动物</option>\n        <option>鸟类</option>\n        <option>爬行动物</option>\n      </select>\n      <button>搜索</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card-container\">\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"\" alt=\"动物图片\">\n        <div class=\"card-content\">\n          <h3>非洲象</h3>\n          <p>类别：哺乳动物</p>\n          <p>栖息地：非洲草原</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"\" alt=\"动物图片\">\n        <div class=\"card-content\">\n          <h3>美洲豹</h3>\n          <p>类别：哺乳动物</p>\n          <p>栖息地：南美雨林</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"list-demo\">\n      <h3>动物叫声示例</h3>\n      <audio controls>\n        <source src=\"animal-sound.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\">\n        浏览器不支持音频播放。\n      </audio>\n\n      <h3>野生动物纪录片</h3>\n      <!-- 在这里添加 video 标签 -->\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <footer>\n    <p>© 2025 野生动物纪录片展示 - 教学用途</p>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "css": "",
    "js": ""
  },
